title: Cutting Seaweed
description: A person wearing a yellow shirt and a clear plastic apron is holding a piece of seaweed with one hand while using scissors to cut it with the other hand. The person is also wearing disposable gloves.

title: Aquatic Plant
description: A vibrant green aquatic plant with elongated, feathery leaves, partially submerged in clear water. The plant exhibits a natural, flowing shape, with some leaves curling and others extending upwards, creating a dynamic visual effect.

title: Microscopic View of Plant Cells
description: This image shows a close-up view of plant cells, highlighting their green chloroplasts. The cells are arranged in a grid-like pattern, with various sizes of chloroplasts visible, indicating the process of photosynthesis.
